Meanwhile in Honduras, it's 1963 and this guy has just staged a military coup to prevent the rise of Communism

00:00:50.460 --> 00:00:52.400
And is now the military leader of the country

00:00:52.540 --> 00:00:56.160
He immediately began harassing the peasants' unions and other left-wing groups

00:00:56.160 --> 00:01:00.620
But he's a little insecure about the legitimacy of his leadership, so he holds an election and wins

00:01:00.629 --> 00:01:04.260
But then the opposing party says, "Hey man, that election was clearly corrupt and fraudulent

00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:08.480
