00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:41.720
So great job at reducing tensions

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:44.960
El Salvador won decisively over the exhausted Hondurans

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:50.120
While spectators battled in the stands, team Honduras fled home in a bulletproof bus with rocks being thrown at them

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:53.560
And the Honduran coach reportedly told his players that they were lucky they lost

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:54.790
In response to the defeat

00:02:54.790 --> 00:02:57.700
Hondurans began terrorising the Salvadoran settlers even more

00:02:57.700 --> 00:03:01.060
In some cases reportedly throwing them off their land and burning down their homes

00:03:01.060 --> 00:03:03.600
And the immigrants began fleeing back to El Salvador

00:03:03.660 --> 00:03:05.960
