00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:06.840
It was close

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:10.540
But El Salvador came out victorious, knocking Honduras out of the tournament

00:03:10.540 --> 00:03:12.620
The atmosphere was riotous, literally

00:03:12.780 --> 00:03:16.080
And back in Honduras attacks on the Salvadoran immigrants further increased

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.800
This was too much for El Salvador to bear, with its people under attack

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:21.660
And an unmanageable refugee crisis on its hands

00:03:21.660 --> 00:03:25.260
El Salvador severed all diplomatic ties with Honduras and declared WAR

00:03:27.300 --> 00:03:31.320
The Football War is also known as the 100 Hours War because that's how long it lasted

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:33.460
Making it one of the shortest wars in history

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:38.960
El Salvador started by carrying out air raids in strat egic locations within Honduras

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:40.820
Including Toncontin International Airport

00:03:40.900 --> 00:03:43.480
Which prevented the Honduran Air Force from getting into the sky

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:49.180
