00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:54.200
Their advance was rapid and they were quickly approaching the Honduran capital

00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:57.160
Then the Organization of American States met in a bit of a panic

00:03:57.160 --> 00:03:59.800
