00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:05.680
So they went to El Salvador and said, "can you please stop invading?"

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:08.560
And El Salvador declared, "NOT UNTIL THEY STOP BEING JERKS!!!!"

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:10.140
And so the war went on

