00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:18.260
They successfully carried out air raids in Salvadoran air bases and oil facilities

00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:21.620
Crippling the Salvadoran supply line and stopping their advance dead

00:04:23.180 --> 00:04:27.000
Caught in a bit of a stalemate, the situation was no longer advantageous to El Salvador

00:04:27.060 --> 00:04:32.580
So when the Organization of American States once again asked them to stop and agreed to ensure the safety of the Salvadoran immigrants

00:04:32.590 --> 00:04:36.220
